Docs.remarks:
This interface provides a mechanism to fetch instances to objects of a given  from classes that implement this interface.

For example the  class implements this and allows fething a few fields that are not exposed by its properties.  




A typical implementation will look like this:

 		object IServiceProvider.GetService (Type service)
		{
			if (service == typeof (Something))
				return something;
			if (service == typeof (DateTime))
				return my_date_time;
		}
